cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an approach to improve the dependability of deep CNNs by reducing misclassification rates and rejecting adversarial examples. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to achieve its goals. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, and cs.NE, in that order.
